<li>交付速度</li>\n<li>叢集優化能力 </li>\n</ul></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><div>\n<hr/></div></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em><strong>Rubin</strong><strong> 平台</strong><strong> =</strong><strong> 供應鏈分水嶺</strong></em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Vera Rubin NVL72：</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul>\n<li>100%Direct Liquid Cooling</li>\n<li> 單 GPU 功耗 2.3kW</li>\n<li> 每櫃價值暴增</li>\n<li>每櫃液冷價值 + 17%</li>\n</ul></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>結論很清楚：</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>沒有 L11 能力的 ODM，未來只能當下游代工</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>能做 L12 的，才有議價權</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><div>\n<hr/></div></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em><strong>二、三大廠定位與投資邏輯</strong></em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><div>\n<hr/></div></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em><strong>鴻海<strong> (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)</strong></strong><strong>：</strong><strong>L10→L12</strong><strong> 一條龍霸主</strong></em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em><strong>產業定位</strong></em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</sect